'''雙層床'''是一個{{le|床架|Bed frame}}分成上下兩層的結構，床架可以是金屬或木製，兩層以梯級連接，上層多有圍欄，下層多為[[單人床|單人床]]，亦可以是[[雙人床|雙人床]]設計。上下層可以是完全重疊或程90度交錯放置，亦有下層沒有床但放置了[[書枱|書枱]]及[[衣櫥|衣櫥]]或[[書架|書架]]的設計<ref>[http://www.elephantstaircase.com/wiki/index.php?title=HowToBuildALoft "How To Build A Dorm Loft"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325085400/http://www.elephantstaircase.com/wiki/index.php?title=HowToBuildALoft |date=2016-03-25 }}, Elephant Staircase</ref><ref>Tim Carter, [http://www.askthebuilder.com/B280_Building_a_Loft_Bed.shtml "Building a Loft Bed"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.askthebuilder.com/B280_Building_a_Loft_Bed.shtml |date=20111116073533 }} and [http://www.askthebuilder.com/printer_280_Build_a_Loft_Bed_for_Any_Bedroom.shtml "Build a Loft Bed"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071025194428/http://www.askthebuilder.com/printer_280_Build_a_Loft_Bed_for_Any_Bedroom.shtml |date=October 25, 2007 }}, Ask The Builder</ref>。由於需要梯級上落，[[美國|美國]]政府不建議6歲以下小孩使用<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cpsc.gov/CPSCPUB/PUBS/5007.html |title=US Consumer Product Safety Commission: CPSC Document #5007 |publisher=Cpsc.gov |access-date=2013-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101216062303/http://cpsc.gov/cpscpub/pubs/5007.html# |archive-date=2010-12-16 }}</ref>。

